These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, go
City: edinburgh, rome, venice
1. the person traveling to rome is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing go is between the person traveling to venice and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Game      | mah-jongg | go | chess |
| City   | rome     | edinburgh    | venice   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, bike
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, water
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking milk and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Transport   | helicopter    | bike        | jet-ski |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | water | milk         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, action, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, march
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person watching thriller movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Movie-Genre   | action | satire     | thriller |
| Birthday        | july  | march | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, spanish, british
3 different games are played: go, backgammon, canasta
1. the turkish is the person playing go##1
2. the british is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing go##2
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Nationality   | spanish  | british     | turkish |
| Game           | backgammon | canasta | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, chestnut, pink
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, indian, dutch
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the canadian is between the dutch and the indian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Color   | chestnut | pink     | lavender |
| Nationality     | dutch    | canadian | indian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different games are played: bridge, domino, whist
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, fonseca, alhambra
1. the blend-smoker is between the person playing whist and the person playing bridge##2
2. the person playing bridge is the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Game   | bridge  | domino   | whist        |
| Cigar         | fonseca | blend | alhambra |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, dancing, board-games
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, orange, coral
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who likes purple is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who likes orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby          | dancing  | camping  | board-games |
| Color   | orange | purple | coral     |

