.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, turtle
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, bike, tram
1. the owner of the frog is the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the turtle##2
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Pet   | turtle   | rabbit  | frog  |
| Transport   | ship | bike | tram |

