.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, november
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, iced-tea
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in november##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday   | march | june   | november   |
| Beverage         | iced-tea  | fanta | mirinda |

