.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daffodil, aconite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, december
1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsaconite and the person who's birthday is in november##2
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Flower      | aconite | daffodil   | lily |
| Birthday   | december  | august | november   |

 